<Layout
  title="ASKO Appliance Repair | (424) 499-7788"
  description="Expert ASKO appliance repair for dishwashers, washers, dryers, laundry appliances, wine climate cabinets, and premium Scandinavian kitchen appliances. Professional ASKO repair, maintenance, and installation support."
  ogImage="/asko/asko-appliance-repair-los-angeles-orange-county-ventura-county.webp"
